cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with image analysis and matching to automatically label actors in TV series. 
2. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also likely as the paper deals with analyzing images and videos from TV series. 
3. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is another possible category as the paper deals with retrieving information about actors from IMDB. 
4. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category as the paper proposes a graph-matching based self-labelling algorithm. 
5. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also a possible category as the paper deals with developing an automated system for labeling actors in TV series.
